            "stanza_text": "Je vous aime, ô jeune fille !\nAussi lorsque je vous vois,\nMon regard de bonheur brille,\nAussi tout mon sang pétille\nLorsque j'entends votre voix."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Douce à mon amour timide,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Vous en accueillez l'aveu,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Mais sans qu'un rayon humide",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Argente votre œil limpide,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Lac pur où dort le ciel bleu.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Douce à mon amour timide,\nVous en accueillez l'aveu,\nMais sans qu'un rayon humide\nArgente votre œil limpide,\nLac pur où dort le ciel bleu."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Pourquoi cette retenue ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Entre nous rien de caché.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "— Enfant ! votre âme ingénue",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Peut se montrer toute nue",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Comme Ève avant le péché.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pourquoi cette retenue ?\nEntre nous rien de caché.\n— Enfant ! votre âme ingénue\nPeut se montrer toute nue\nComme Ève avant le péché."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "C'est un amour sans mélange",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Que l'amour que j'ai pour vous,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Frais comme au cœur la louange,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Ardent à toucher un ange,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Pur à rendre Dieu jaloux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C'est un amour sans mélange\nQue l'amour que j'ai pour vous,\nFrais comme au cœur la louange,\nArdent à toucher un ange,\nPur à rendre Dieu jaloux."
